{"tid":941320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支那專用ios?】蘋果下周為中國用戶更新軟件以解決法律合規問題","createTime":"2018-12-14T16:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T04:35:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"835ea92f0fa43f1ea33e0efe03b351f49048e4f6","tid":941320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"外電引述蘋果公司聲明指，下周初將為中國iPhone用戶更新軟件，以解決可能存在的法律合規問題及任何對合規性的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果與高通的專利糾紛持續近兩年，中國福州市中級人民法院近日對蘋果部分舊款iPhone機型頒布銷售禁令，因為涉及侵犯高通兩項專利。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果指，尊重福州法院的裁定，但集團會申請覆議，這屬提出上訴的第一步。蘋果又說，相信現時在中國出售的iPhone機型的合規性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433319-20181214.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433319-20181214.htm&d=AdcSeeH524k86dmvdXGFvG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a3716d4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1433319-20181214.htm&h=e0d1a507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1433319-20181214.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4f8572737b191f21e4d70f0a52bd9f6450bc4755","tid":941320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5080f963294451467289efa82936176f34bbcb","tid":941320,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"將高通告佢個堆function disable曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b16c26feae75177725ec29e7b4b7ea1a2ed288","tid":941320,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T16:28:25.000Z","msg":"香港再唔獨立遲早有日就會燒到埋身"},{"pid":"147d080b54af4e6cf2e462cb9cf45cff4c5d5c7b","tid":941320,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score